(This course provides a comprehensive understanding of RESTful API design and) Tj
T* (implementation. It covers the foundational concepts of REST architecture, including its core) Tj
T* (constraints, and delves into HTTP fundamentals essential for API development. Key aspects) Tj
T* (include resource modeling, URI design, data formats like JSON, and advanced topics such as) Tj
T* (API versioning, documentation with OpenAPI, and robust testing strategies. A significant portion) Tj
T* (is dedicated to API security, encompassing authentication \(OAuth2, JWT\), authorization, CORS,) Tj
T* (rate limiting, and protection against common web vulnerabilities. The course aims to equip) Tj
T* (students with the knowledge to design, build, and secure scalable and maintainable RESTful) Tj
T* (APIs.) Tj
ET
